            <div class="main-bd">

                <h2><a href="https://book.douban.com/review/1717057/">一点感慨</a></h2>

                <div id="review_1717057_short" class="review-short" data-rid="1717057">
                    <div class="short-content">

                        不读三毛的书很多年，我并不是很老，只是用带着沧桑的语气说了这么一句话。《万水千山走遍》不容易，虽然是很多人梦寐以求的事情，一个人一辈子总也呆在一个地方很正常，老一辈的人不都是这么过来的吗。当年读三毛小小震撼的是她与我的父母几乎同龄，获得的生活却是那么截然而...

                        &nbsp;(<a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-1717057-copy" class="unfold" title="展开">展开</a>)
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div id="review_1717057_full" class="hidden">
                    <div id="review_1717057_full_content" class="full-content"></div>
                </div>

                <div class="action">
                    <a href="javascript:;" class="action-btn up" data-rid="1717057" title="有用">
                        <img src="https://img1.doubanio.com/f/zerkalo/536fd337139250b5fb3cf9e79cb65c6193f8b20b/pics/up.png" />
                        <span id="r-useful_count-1717057">
                                3
                        </span>
                    </a>
                    <a href="javascript:;" class="action-btn down" data-rid="1717057" title="没用">
                        <img src="https://img1.doubanio.com/f/zerkalo/68849027911140623cf338c9845893c4566db851/pics/down.png" />
                        <span id="r-useless_count-1717057">
                        </span>
                    </a>
                    <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/1717057/#comments" class="reply ">0回应</a>

                    <a href="javascript:;;" class="fold hidden">收起</a>
                </div>
            </div>
